<section id="definition-list">

    <div class="container">

		<h3>Definition List</h3>
		<p>Definition lists, <code>dl</code>, have margins set to maintain vertical rhythm. Definition terms show in <strong>bold</strong>, and descriptions are offset for visual separation. Definition terms preceeded by a description have a top margin.</p>

		<div class="example">

			<dl>
				<dt>Definition term</dt>
				<dd>Definition description</dd>

				<dt>Definition term</dt>
				<dd>Definition description</dd>
				<dd>Definition description</dd>

				<dt>Definition term</dt>
				<dt>Definition term</dt>
				<dd>Definition description</dd>
			</dl>

		</div>

		<pre class="example-code"><code class="language-markup">&lt;dl&gt;
